            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Cuomo deserves the criticism. However, there is some serious hypocrisy at play here. Amid an outcry about nursing home deaths, these same Republican critics copied and pasted Cuomo’s infamous nursing home immunity law into their own legislation.",
